					<h1>Recovery Act Oversight</h1>
						
						<a href="http://www.recovery.gov" target="_blank"><img style="width: 140px;" src="/images/recoveryLogo.jpg" alt="Recovery Act Oversight Logo" class="rClean" /></a>
					
					<p>
					OIG's duties under the Inspector General Act of 1978 include oversight over programs funded through the <a class="exit" target="_blank"	href="http://www.recovery.gov/">American Recovery and Reinvestment Act of 2009 (Recovery Act)</a>.
					</p>

			
<p> OIG will assess whether HHS is using Recovery Act funds in accordance with legal and administrative requirements and is meeting the accountability objectives defined by the Office of Management and Budget (OMB). </p>
			
