					<h2 id="ivestigative" class="acc_trigger"><a name="investigative"></a><a href="#">Investigative Activities</a></h2>
					<div class="acc_container">
							<div class="block">
							<p> OIG and its special agents will: </p>
<ul>
  <li> investigate individuals and organizations who knowingly and willfully execute schemes to defraud any HHS program, grant, or contract involving Recovery Act funds; and </li>
  <li> facilitate ongoing communications with Federal, State, and local law enforcement and other agencies regarding the use and distribution of HHS Recovery Act funds. </li>
</ul>
					
